useful for quick trials but should not be the rollout target for a stable environment. For the strictest rollout, deploy `ghcr.io/<owner>/<repo>/ingest-service@sha256:<digest>`."},"77":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-32","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#container-image","content":"The container publishing workflow runs after the `CI` workflow succeeds on `main`, so the image is gated by package verification, Docker Compose validation, Helm render/lint checks, and Docker-backed E2E tests."},"78":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-33","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#clickhouse-cloud","content":"ClickHouse Cloud works with the same ingest service configuration. The service uses the official `@clickhouse/client` package and passes `CLICKHOUSE_URL`, `CLICKHOUSE_USER`, `CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD`, and `CLICKHOUSE_DATABASE` directly to the client. No code change is required for a Cloud service as long as the URL is the HTTPS endpoint for the ClickHouse HTTP interface."},"79":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-34","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#clickhouse-cloud","content":"Use the connection details from the ClickHouse Cloud service connection menu. For the Node.js or HTTPS connection form, the URL usually has this shape:"},"80":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-35","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#clickhouse-cloud","content":"Then configure the ingest service the same way you would for a self-hosted production deployment:"},"81":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-36","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#clickhouse-cloud","content":"Run migrations from a trusted environment that can reach the ClickHouse Cloud service:"},"82":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-37","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#clickhouse-cloud","content":"The browser SDK and React package do not connect to ClickHouse Cloud directly. They should continue to send events to the ingest service `apiHost`; the ingest service is the only component that needs ClickHouse Cloud credentials."},"83":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-38","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#environment-variables","content":"Variable"},"84":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-39","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#environment-variables","content":"Required"},"85":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-40","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#environment-variables","content":"Default"},"86":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-41","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#environment-variables","content":"Purpose"},"87":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-42","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#environment-variables","content":"`HOST`"},"88":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-43","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#environment-variables","content":"no"},"89":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-44","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#environment-variables","content":"`0.0.0.0`"},"90":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-45","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#environment-variables","content":"HTTP listen host."},"91":{"id":"/deployment/docker-compose-46","page_id":"/deployment/docker-compose","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/deployment/docker-compose#environment-variables","con