` values because Next.js inlines `basePath` during static export. The workflow deploys the production docs for `main` and publishes same-repository PR previews under `/pr-preview/pr-<number>/` when both the PR and its latest push changed docs-related files. Locally, the repo verifies the presence and wiring of docs files during E2E. The actual rendered Pages build is validated by GitHub Actions."},"554":{"id":"/project/verification-56","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"The CI workflow at `.github/workflows/ci.yml` runs package verification, Docker Compose validation, Helm chart lint/render checks, and the Docker-backed E2E suite. The container workflow at `.github/workflows/container.yml` builds and publishes the ingest image to GitHub Container Registry only after CI succeeds on `main`."},"555":{"id":"/project/verification-57","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Validate deployment artifacts locally with:"},"556":{"id":"/project/verification-58","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Run the local ingest benchmark with:"},"557":{"id":"/project/verification-59","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Package publishability is checked with:"},"558":{"id":"/project/verification-60","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#when-to-add-e2e-coverage","content":"Add E2E assertions when documentation introduces a new public workflow, API shape, query pattern, or deployment guarantee. Unit tests are enough for internal helpers, but anything shown in `/docs` should either be exercised by `npm run verify:e2e` or explicitly documented as a static/CI-only check."},"559":{"id":"/refere